OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FA husband "casually walked off down
OL,8,Fthe street" after stabbing his wife to
OL,9,Fdeath in broad daylight and leaving
OL,10,Ftheir baby son behind, a court has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FA witness said Habibur Masum, 26,
OL,14,Fthrew the knife away before "dusting
OL,15,Fhis hands and calmly carrying on" as
OL,16,Fhis wife, Kulsuma Akter, was lying in
OL,17,Fthe street.
