OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FThe jury heard Masum tracked his wife
OL,8,FMs Akter, 27, to a refuge in Bradford
OL,9,Fwhere she had been staying to escape
OL,10,Fhis "violence, jealousy and
OL,11,Fcontrolling behaviour."
OL,13,FMs Akter had left the hostel to go out
OL,14,Fwith a friend on 6 April 2024,
OL,15,Fbelieving Masum was in Spain, when he
OL,16,Fconfronted her in the street whilst
OL,17,Fshe was pushing their seven-month-old
OL,18,Fson in a pram.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/10
