OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FA friend of Ms Akter's from the refuge
OL,8,Fsaid Masum had tracked his wife
OL,9,Fthrough her phone location, which she
OL,10,Fhad forgotten to turn off when she
OL,11,Fleft their home.
OL,13,FProsecutors say the knife attack left
OL,14,Fher with multiple stab injuries,
OL,15,Fincluding one which severed the
OL,16,Fjugular vein in her neck.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/10
