OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FMasum denies murdering Ms Akter but
OL,8,Fhas pleaded guilty to manslaughter and
OL,9,Fpossession of a knife. He also denies
OL,10,Ftwo charges of assault, one count of
OL,11,Fmaking threats to kill and one charge
OL,12,Fof stalking.
OL,14,FOne witness speaking at Bradford Crown
OL,15,FCourt described hearing Ms Akter
OL,16,F"screaming in agony and pain".
OL,18,FHe said he was walking in the area and
OL,19,Fsaw what looked like a man trying to
OL,20,Fdrag a woman off a pram and "punching
OL,21,Fher in the abdomen".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
