OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FThe statement read: "I did step
OL,8,Fforward to see if I could help the
OL,9,Fwoman but then I realised he had a
OL,10,Fknife in his hand.
OL,12,F"I didn't see the knife or blood but I
OL,13,Fsaw the stabbing motion which made it
OL,14,Fobvious he was stabbing her. He then
OL,15,Foverpowered her and threw her down in
OL,16,Ffront of a car.
OL,18,F"The female was still screaming and
OL,19,Fthen the screaming stopped. Within
OL,20,Fseconds, the guy stood up and walked
OL,21,Foff down the street.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/10
