OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,F"At that point I wasn't sure if this
OL,8,Fwas a male stabbing random people so I
OL,9,Fturned my family round and started
OL,10,Fwalking back to our home address.
OL,12,F"I kept an eye on the male as I was
OL,13,Fconcerned for my family. I saw him
OL,14,Fthrow what I assumed was the weapon
OL,15,Fover a fence.
OL,17,F"He then dusted his hands and calmly
OL,18,Fcarried on walking."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
