OL,7,FAnother woman said she was in a car
OL,8,Fwhen she heard screaming and saw a man
OL,9,Fstabbing a woman. Her statement
OL,10,Fdescribed how she saw the woman
OL,11,Ffalling to the floor and the man
OL,12,F"casually walking down the street"
OL,13,Fbefore throwing the knife away.
OL,15,FPrevious threats
OL,17,FThe court heard Ms Akter had been
OL,18,Fmoved from her home in Oldham to the
OL,19,Frefuge in January 2024 after she told
OL,20,Fpolice that Masum had assaulted her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/10
