OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FJurors heard that Ms Akter reported a
OL,8,Fknife being held to her throat as
OL,9,FMasum threatened to kill her over a
OL,10,F"completely innocuous" message she
OL,11,Freceived from a male colleague.
OL,13,FIn a statement she made to police at
OL,14,Fthe time, Ms Akter said: "I was very
OL,15,Ffrightened when he was holding the
OL,16,Fknife as I believed what he was
OL,17,Ftelling me and that he might kill me.
OL,18,FI do not want to stay with him
OL,19,Fanymore."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/10
