OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FShe told officers that her 18-month
OL,8,Frelationship with Masum was "usually
OL,9,Fgood" but that "recently he has been
OL,10,Fcontrolling me... taking my phone off
OL,11,Fme and not letting me contact anyone."
OL,13,FIn a police interview played in court,
OL,14,Fa friend of Ms Akter said she had told
OL,15,Fher they got married in Bangladesh and
OL,16,Fit was a "love marriage".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/10
