OL,3,CCourt told husband 'calmly carried on'
OL,4,Cafter fatally stabbing wife in the
OL,5,Cstreet
OL,7,FIn a short opening address to jurors,
OL,8,FFrida Hussain KC, defending Masum,
OL,9,Fsaid: "You will need to consider
OL,10,Fwhether he attacked her because he was
OL,11,Ftriggered by something that she said
OL,12,For did that caused him to lose his
OL,13,Fself-control."
OL,15,FShe told the jury they would also need
OL,16,Fto consider whether he was "suffering
OL,17,Ffrom an abnormality of mental
OL,18,Ffunction" at the time.
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
